imdb.plot outline: ShadowTrader Uncovered is your chance to see your two favorite Shadowtraders live every day. From swing trading, to what happened in the earlier hours of the trading day, to interactive stock challenge updates, Peter and Brad bring a full hour of trading talk exclusively to the tastytrade network. Watch the team live from Philadelphia as they bring you more technical analysis, market profiles and sector rotation strategy that could only come from the Shadowtraders.
